==== (% style=&amp;#34;font-family:~&amp;#34;Times New Roman~&amp;#34;&amp;#34; %)(B.) Nationalist scapegoating precludes anti-capitalist mobilization ~-~~-~- CFIUS allows all the problems of capitalism to be blamed on China.(%%) ====

