=== 2AC Guidance ===

==== The plan is guidance not legislation ====

(% class=&amp;#34;MsoNormal&amp;#34; %)
(% class=&amp;#34;StyleStyleBold12pt&amp;#34; style=&amp;#34;font-size:13.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt&amp;#34; %)Jackson 10(%%) ((% style=&amp;#34;font-size: 10.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt&amp;#34; %)James K. Jackson, CRS Specialist in International Trade and Finance, Foreign Investment, CFIUS, and Homeland Security: An Overview, February 4,   http:~/~/fpc.state.gov/documents/organization/138597.pdf)

(% class=&amp;#34;MsoNormal&amp;#34; %)
 

(% class=&amp;#34;MsoNormal&amp;#34; %)
(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt&amp;#34; %)While (% class=&amp;#34;StyleBoldUnderline&amp;#34; style=&amp;#34;background:yellow; mso-highlight:yellow&amp;#34; %)CFIUS(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;background:yellow;mso-highlight:yellow&amp;#34; %)’s(% style=&amp;#34;font-size:8.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt&amp;#34; %) activities often seem to be quite opaque, … under foreign control, (% class=&amp;#34;StyleBoldUnderline&amp;#34; %)primarily for national defense purposes.

==== That means no link ====

